OL,7,FA care home worker who gave the wrong
OL,8,Fmedication to a resident who later
OL,9,Fdied has been acquitted of
OL,10,Fmanslaughter, police said.
OL,12,FJane Barnard, 66, denied killing Derek
OL,13,FDavies, 75, who lived at the care home
OL,14,Fwhere she was employed, Wheatridge
OL,15,FCourt in Abbeydale, Gloucester, and
OL,16,Fdied on September 8 2021.
