OL,7,FMr Davies died after Barnard
OL,8,Fmistakenly gave him medication
OL,9,Fprescribed for another resident, Jason
OL,10,FDodsworth, including 90mg of slow-
OL,11,Frelease morphine.
OL,13,FBarnard previously pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fone count of wilful neglect of Mr
OL,15,FDavies, contrary to the Criminal
OL,16,FJustice and Courts Act 2015.
OL,18,FGloucestershire Police said she would
OL,19,Fbe sentenced for this offence on
OL,20,FJanuary 19.
