OL,7,FIn a statement issued by the force
OL,8,Ffollowing the verdict, Mr Davies'
OL,9,Ffamily said: "The last four years
OL,10,Fsince our dad's death have been
OL,11,Fextremely upsetting for our family,
OL,12,Fboth because we have missed him
OL,13,Fterribly and because we have had to
OL,14,Flive without knowing what caused his
OL,15,Fdeath and how it occurred.
OL,26,@qD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
