OL,7,F"Going through this has been traumatic
OL,8,Ffor everyone involved ` our dad and
OL,9,Ffamily, as well as the defendant and
OL,10,Fher family ` there are no winners here.
OL,12,F"We don't know how much more time we
OL,13,Fwould have had with our dad but these
OL,14,Fevents robbed us of that precious time
OL,15,Fand he is greatly missed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
