OL,7,F"We are thankful for the hard work and
OL,8,Feffort that has been put into this by
OL,9,Fthe police and Crown Prosecution
OL,10,FService, and we hope with the closure
OL,11,Fof this trial and with key questions
OL,12,Fanswered, that we can start to process
OL,13,Fwhat happened and to remember dad for
OL,14,Fthe person he was."
OL,16,FDuring the trial, jurors heard how
OL,17,FBarnard wrongly gave Mr Davies 90g of
OL,18,Fslow-release morphine, which was
OL,19,Fprescribed for Mr Dodsworth.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@SO]
