OL,7,FAfter realising her mistake, Barnard
OL,8,Ffailed to report it and lied to
OL,9,Fcolleagues and medical professional to
OL,10,Fconceal what she had done, even after
OL,11,FMr Davies fell ill and was taken to
OL,12,Fhospital, the court heard.
OL,14,FShe disposed of the medication Mr
OL,15,FDavies should have received and
OL,16,Fpretended the medication she did give
OL,17,Fhim had been dropped down the sink.
OL,19,FMr Davies became unwell later that
OL,20,Fafternoon and Barnard called 999 for
OL,21,Fan ambulance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
