OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Bernadette Harding,
OL,8,Fof Gloucestershire Police, said: "Mr
OL,9,FDavies' family have been waiting four
OL,10,Fyears to find out the full details
OL,11,Fabout what happened to their father,
OL,12,Fand I thank them for their patience
OL,13,Fthroughout this.
OL,15,F"They have sat through the entire
OL,16,Ftrial and have been nothing but
OL,17,Frespectful and dignified for the whole
OL,18,Fprocess.
OL,26,@pD@bOUwD@AOU
