OL,7,F"Nothing will bring Mr Davies back,
OL,8,Fbut I hope this process means they now
OL,9,Fhave the answers they wanted and
OL,10,Fdeserved.
OL,12,F"Mr Davies deserved to be cared for
OL,13,Fproperly, and he should have been safe
OL,14,Fin the environment in which he was
OL,15,Fliving.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
